{
  "texts": [
    "CFP students held favorable views regarding the implementation of ChatGPT.",
    "More precisely, we observed significant improvements in the perceived usefulness, perceived ease of use, and intention to use.",
    "The effect size of the observed enhancements was moderate, indicating that there was a noticeable influence.",
    "Although the findings fail to demonstrate a statistically significant improvement in their inclination towards utilizing ChatGPT, To summarize, the implementation of the intervention led to enhanced attitudes and intentions towards the utilization of ChatGPT.",
    "Nevertheless, this did not yield a substantial influence on the perception of utilizing ChatGPT."
  ]
}